Package it.dc.bridge.om

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CoAPInterface
    The CoAPInterface is an AllJoyn interface implemented by the AllJoyn objects representing a CoAP resource.
    CoAPRequestMessage
    The CoAP request message interface.
    CoAPResponseMessage
    The CoAP response message interface.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AJObjectManagerApp
    AJObjectManager is the AllJoyn class that provides the CoAP resources to the AJ network.
    BridgeAboutData
    The class implements the AboutDataListener interface, that supplies the list of properties required for Announce signal payload.
    CoAP
    CoAP defines the RequestCode and ResponseCode constants.
    CoAPResource
    The Class CoAPResource is an AllJoyn object representing the CoAP resource.
    Options
    The Options class is a collection of CoAP option fields.
    RequestMessage
    The Class RequestMessage is used in the AllJoyn message exchanges.
    ResponseMessage
    The Class ResponseMessage is used in the AllJoyn message exchanges.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CoAP.RequestCode
    The enumeration of request codes: GET, POST, PUT and DELETE.
    CoAP.ResponseCode
    The enumeration of response codes.
